{"tid":590800,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"樂視體育遭兩公司申請清盤","createTime":"2018-03-13T03:15:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-13T03:55:11.000Z","uid":39464,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"6bc18a044bf4fa8be92a34ad562bd85810bcb8cf","tid":590800,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T03:15:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180313/large/1520909979_2826.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180313%2Flarge%2F1520909979_2826.jpg&h=3fd50f1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日兩度未能為用戶提供訊號的「樂視體育香港」（下稱樂視），遭兩間經營運動節目版權生意的公司向本港法院呈請清盤，案件並已排期於5月16日上午提訊。<br />\n<br />\n兩公司分別為位於新加坡和愛爾蘭的MP &amp; Silva Pte Lte及Media Partners &amp; Silva Ltd，申請樂視體育文化產業發展（香港）有限公司（現稱香港體育產業發展有限公司）清盤。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180313/57939498\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180313%2F57939498&d=M2J4%2BtcXLJ4gd8wtiZWwY0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=17eb66e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180313%2F57939498&h=f7144ad4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180313/57939498</a>"},{"pid":"4289575d9edd0303d4b5a413f3a1d93f38c04415","tid":590800,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T03:16:32.000Z","msg":"買起香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54668072b8aceae4c3d0cf5334b9683d430938ad","tid":590800,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T03:23:21.000Z","msg":"【樂視熄燈】英超冇得播 冇錢交租 傳業主周四上門封舖<br />\n<br />\n「樂視體育香港」（下稱樂視）在剛過去的周末未能提供英超直播後，有傳周四將封鋪「熄機」，停止運作；而據悉now TV已獲准製作英超節目，有可能臨時「接手」續播今季餘下的英超。<br />\n<br />\n今季多次傳出財困的樂視，在剛過去的周末都未能向樂視用戶提供英超直播，惹來大量投訴，但樂視一直未有回應。到今日傍晚就再傳出內部員工消息，指樂視除未能支付租用網絡商的雲端網絡費用，引致周末多場英超未能直播外，位處荃灣的樂視總部亦因長期拖欠租金，業主決定會在周四晚上門「封舖」，故周四晚將是樂視的最後一晚。而now TV內部已通知旗下員工，今周可能開始接手製作及直播英超。<br />\n樂視目前只餘英超及NBA兩個賽事的直播權，兩個賽事已支付大部份的版權費，只是一直拖欠租用網絡商的網絡費，加上未繳付辦公室的租金，就算早前將今夏俄羅斯世界盃決賽周售給電訊盈科旗下的now TV，仍未能解決財務問題，目前亦未知道如何向訂購樂視體育服務的用戶善後。<br />\n消息指，樂視仍有現金出今個月的薪金，這兩日將通知員工回公司領取工資；目前樂視除英超已獲now TV「接手」外，其另一主打NBA亦去向未卜。部份評述員表示，仍未收到最新消息，未來幾天仍有直播下，會如常上班。由於NBA快將進入季後賽，不少「苦主」除在樂視的fb留言，指收看不到英超要回水外，亦有不少人查詢NBA直播節目的動向。（詳見另文：【樂視熄燈】用戶吶喊 fb苦主大聯盟吐苦水 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2p8QDjZ）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2p8QDjZ%EF%BC%89&d=M2J4%2BtcXLJ4gd8wtiZWwY0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=e6e361e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2p8QDjZ）</a><br />\n記者：曾雁平<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180312/57938084\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180312%2F57938084&d=M2J4%2BtcXLJ4gd8wtiZWwY0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=6882447a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180312%2F57938084&h=68c13c2f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180312/57938084</a>"},{"pid":"328c2d25f6a030012af9d58f98931abc26836cc5","tid":590800,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T03:24:07.000Z","msg":"訂咗嗰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2796aca365ccc543d91995590bfe59066e7283d3","tid":590800,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T03:24:24.000Z","msg":"燒山有冇份？"},{"pid":"05562975123cd405ebed82becc4a9bcd61dd64e3","tid":590800,"uid":10671,"like":1,"dislike":0,